title: The Beatles - Earlier...A Compilation
description:
A lossless compilation of earlier Beatles music.  I made this for myself from various sources but maybe other folks would be interested.  Of course there's stuff either included or excluded that will be divisive but again this was for me and my taste.  These can fit onto 2 discs at about one hour each.  I hope you enjoy.
